If you had one wish what would YOU wish for? What would ANYONE wish for? Well, in Eight Billion Genies, we sure find out. Join us as we cover this epic tale of wish fulfillment, desire, restraint, and self-worth as we tackle this absolute INSTANT CLASSIC from Charles Soule with art by Ryan Browne.

